For the SRI.COM domain, we do use the serial number which consists of the
date of last modification plus and edit number for that day (for those rare
occasions that the domain changes several times).  We have configured it
such that it is always increasing in value.

I believe that everyone should maintain that field since it should come into
play more in the future as we distribute SOA's further.

-dle
